A copy of this license is provided in the file gpl.txt.


=== Platforms ===

SciDAVis runs on GNU/Linux, Windows and MacOS X; 
possibly also on other platforms like *BSD.


=== Installation ===

See INSTALL.html


=== Web site ===

http://scidavis.sourceforge.net


